phrs.translation: 臂神经丛, 翻译, 臂丛神经

sentences.sentence: There was a mild mass effect on the brachialis and pronator teres muscles.
sentences.translation: 肿块轻度影响了肱肌和旋前圆肌，并向后压迫正中神经。

sentences.sentence: Objective: To study the morphological character of the brachialis branches of radial nerve.
sentences.translation: 目的：研究桡神经的肱肌支的形态特点。

sentences.sentence: Objective: to study the anatomical characteristics of the brachialis branches of radial nerve.
sentences.translation: 目的：研究桡神经肱肌支的解剖特点。
